## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **tofersen Qalsody 2023** = first FDA SOD1 ASO ALS — accelerated approval based on NfL plasma biomarker (Quanterix Simoa) without clinical endpoint. VALOR Phase 3 missed primary ALSFRS-R but NfL drop sufficient. quantum-VQE 의 ASO target seed + SOD1 misfolding pocket 가 직접 fit.
2. **AMX0035 Relyvrio 2022 → 2024 withdrawn** = second FDA ALS approval (sodium phenylbutyrate + taurursodiol) but PHOENIX Phase 3 confirmatory fail → manufacturer Amylyx voluntary withdrawal 2024. accelerated approval failure 사례.
3. **edaravone Radicava 2017 IV → 2022 oral** = first FDA antioxidant ALS — Japanese MCI-186 free radical scavenger. IV burdensome → 2022 oral suspension approval improved compliance.
4. **riluzole Rilutek 1995** = first FDA ALS approval — glutamate antagonist (NMDA + AMPA + voltage Na channel). 만성 modest survival benefit 3 month. 30년 paradigm.
5. **BIIB078 C9orf72 ASO Phase 1 fail 2022** = Biogen termination — C9orf72 G4C2 repeat ASO 적응 어려움. Phase 1 efficacy 부족 + 부작용. small-molecule + RAN-translation 차단 paradigm shift 필요.
6. **nusinersen Spinraza 2016 + Zolgensma 2019 + risdiplam 2020** = SMA gene therapy paradigm — first ASO (nusinersen) + first AAV9 (Zolgensma) + first oral splice mod (risdiplam) 동일 disease 3 modality 모두 FDA 승인. ALS ASO + AAV bridge model.
7. **jacifusen 2020 (research)** = Boston Children's individualized FUS ASO n-of-1. patient-specific pre-mRNA ASO. n-of-1 model — Mila (Batten CLN7) 2018 다음 ALS adaptation.
8. **ION363 (Ionis FUS Phase 3)** = jacifusen 후 commercialized FUS ASO Phase 3. 일반 FUS-ALS adaptation.
9. **AMT-162 uniQure** = SOD1 AAV intrathecal gene therapy research — tofersen ASO 후 single-dose alternative.
10. **wet-lab + 임상 RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, ALS 임상 의미 한정. NfL biomarker accelerated approval 사례 (tofersen 2023) 가 quantum-only roadmap 의 in-silico → biomarker bridge 가능성 제시.
11. **HDAC6 = ALS motor neuron axonal transport 회복 paradigm** — SOD1/TDP-43 mutant motor neuron 의 axonal transport defect (Van Den Bosch + d'Ydewalle 학계, KU Leuven) 가 잘 알려진 ALS 메커니즘. tubastatin-A / ACY-738 / ricolinostat ALS preclinical 다수, AGT-100216 (Augustine Therapeutics, 본래 CMT 적응증, 말초 한정 non-hydroxamate, Phase 1 FIH 2025-05) 가 ALS adapt 잠재. **본 roadmap 결정**: CMT 의 말초 한정 paradigm (P-gp substrate by polar acid) 과 ALS 의 CNS-penetrant 요구가 정반대 → **`hxq-als-hd6-001` 별도 ID 분기** (CMT 후보의 polar acid → methyl 치환, heavy 20, lipophilic 강화). non-hydroxamate ZBG + HDAC1/2/3 selectivity ≥1000 + reversible + 자율신경/인지 audit 유지. cross-link `.roadmap.disease_cmt_specific`.
12. **SARM1 = ALS Wallerian-like 축삭변성 공통 경로 paradigm** — Wallerian 축삭변성의 master executioner SARM1 (TIR domain NAD+ hydrolase). ALS motor neuron axon + CMT2 axonal + CIPN 모두 공유 target. Lilly (Disarm 인수) + Nuro Bio Phase 1/discovery — ALS 임상 진입. **본 roadmap 결정**: TIR/ARM pocket 동일 + CMT chemotype `hxq-cmt-sar1-001` (quinazolinone, heavy 17, IP-회피) 그대로 사용 가능. **`hxq-als-sar1-001` 별도 ID 분기 = BBB audit tracking 용** (chemotype 동일, separate ID 는 ALS-specific 임상 endpoint + BBB 침투 검증 audit 분리). cross-link `.roadmap.disease_cmt_specific` + `.roadmap.disease_chronic_neuropathic_pain_specific` + `.roadmap.disease_oncology_supportive_care` (CIPN).
13. **`hxq-als-c9orf72-001` = ALS-specific small-mol paradigm shift** — BIIB078 (Biogen C9orf72 ASO Phase 1 fail 2022) 후 small-molecule + RAN-translation 차단 paradigm 필요. G4C2 repeat secondary structure (G-quadruplex / hairpin) selective binder OR poly-GP/GA/GR/PR/PA dipeptide repeat 생산 차단. scaffold class TBD — Phase β specify. CMT 무관 (ALS-specific).
14. **TDP-43 cryptic exon paradigm — STMN2 + ATXN2 + UNC13A** (v4 RIBOZYME 강화) — TDP-43 LoF 시 발생하는 cryptic exon inclusion → STMN2 (Stathmin-2 축삭재생) / UNC13A (시냅스 release) / ATXN2 (polyQ TDP-43 modifier) 비정상 splicing. QurAlis QRL-101 (STMN2 ASO Phase 2, Biogen 협력) + Stanford-Lilly ATXN2 ASO Phase 1/2 = TDP-43 직접 readout best-in-class mechanism. RIBOZYME axis ASO-only paradigm 탈피 — splice-modulator (risdiplam-class) + RNA-editing (ADAR allele-specific TDP-43) 후속 design 권장. cross-link `.roadmap.disease_hereditary_ataxia_specific` (SCA2 ATXN2 polyQ).
15. **KIF5A axonal kinesin = ALS-CMT2 monogenic 중첩** (v4 axonal cluster 보강) — KIF5A heavy chain 변이는 ALS (탈축삭) + CMT2 (탈축삭) + spastic paraplegia 모두 유발 — 같은 유전자 다중 표현형. anterograde 축삭 수송의 master motor protein → HDAC6 (α-tubulin track 회복) + SARM1 (Wallerian 차단) + KIF5A (motor protein 안정화) = **3-way axonal rescue cluster**. cross-link `.roadmap.disease_cmt_specific` 강화. TBK1/OPTN(autophagy) + GLT-1/EAAT2(글루타민산 청소) 도 §1 표 comparator 로 land — 단일유전자 cluster + 시냅스/glia paradigm 보강.
16. **v5 Q+RB axis 후보 직접 land — KIF5A/STMN2/ATXN2/TBK1 4 candidate** (2026-05-10) — v4 까지 RB axis 는 "다양화 언급" 만 + Q axis 는 KIF5A/TBK1 미등록 gap. v5 에서 직접 hxq-als-* ID 4개 land: `hxq-als-kif5a-001` (Q axis, 축삭 3-way rescue 완성), `hxq-als-stmn2-001` (RB axis, TDP-43 cryptic exon ASO QurAlis QRL-101 paradigm), `hxq-als-atxn2-001` (RB axis, polyQ ataxin-2 ASO Stanford-Lilly paradigm), `hxq-als-tbk1-001` (Q axis, LoF rescue chaperone). **honest disclaimer**: KIF5A scaffold class = kinesin chemistry novel (선례 부족), TBK1 LoF rescue = discovery-stage chemistry novel (LoF 활성 회복은 약리학적으로 도전적 — Phase β 에서 가능성 audit). STMN2/ATXN2 ASO = 표준 gapmer 18-mer (PS+MOE) paradigm.
17. **wet-lab + 임상 0건 disclaimer 유지** — v1-v5 all in-silico DESIGN/schematic. 8 hxq-als-* ID land 가 의미하는 것 = SSOT 명명 + 5-axis 매트릭스 자리 + falsifier ID slot. 실제 Hamiltonian build / VQE / wet-lab 검증 = Phase β-ε 에서 진행 (현재 0건). NfL biomarker accelerated approval (tofersen 2023) = quantum-only roadmap → biomarker bridge 가능성 제시.

